  <entry>
    <title>初始化配置CentOS 7</title>
    <link href="/2024/11/21/%E5%88%9D%E5%A7%8B%E5%8C%96%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AECentOS7/"/>
    <url>/2024/11/21/%E5%88%9D%E5%A7%8B%E5%8C%96%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AECentOS7/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="1-初始化配置CentOS-7"><a href="#1-初始化配置CentOS-7" class="headerlink" title="1. 初始化配置CentOS 7"></a>1. 初始化配置CentOS 7</h1><h2 id="1-1-配置YUM"><a href="#1-1-配置YUM" class="headerlink" title="1.1. 配置YUM"></a>1.1. 配置YUM</h2><h3 id="1-1-1-仅安装64位软件包"><a href="#1-1-1-仅安装64位软件包" class="headerlink" title="1.1.1. 仅安装64位软件包"></a>1.1.1. 仅安装64位软件包</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;exclude=*.i386 *.i586 *.i686&quot;</span> &gt;&gt; /etc/yum.conf<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-1-2-强制YUM使用IPv4"><a href="#1-1-2-强制YUM使用IPv4" class="headerlink" title="1.1.2. 强制YUM使用IPv4"></a>1.1.2. 强制YUM使用IPv4</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;ip_resolve=4&#x27;</span> &gt;&gt; /etc/yum.conf<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="1-2-更新系统"><a href="#1-2-更新系统" class="headerlink" title="1.2. 更新系统"></a>1.2. 更新系统</h2><h3 id="1-2-1-YUM换源"><a href="#1-2-1-YUM换源" class="headerlink" title="1.2.1. YUM换源"></a>1.2.1. YUM换源</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">mv</span> /etc/yum.repos.d/CentOS-Base.repo /etc/yum.repos.d/CentOS-Base.repo.bak<br><br><span class="hljs-built_in">cat</span> &lt;&lt;<span class="hljs-string">EOF &gt; /etc/yum.repos.d/CentOS-Base.repo</span><br><span class="hljs-string">[base]</span><br><span class="hljs-string">name=CentOS-\$releasever - Base</span><br><span class="hljs-string">baseurl=https://mirrors.aliyun.com/centos/\$releasever/os/\$basearch/</span><br><span class="hljs-string">gpgcheck=1</span><br><span class="hljs-string">gpgkey=file:///etc/pki/rpm-gpg/RPM-GPG-KEY-CentOS-7</span><br><span class="hljs-string"></span><br><span class="hljs-string">[updates]</span><br><span class="hljs-string">name=CentOS-\$releasever - Updates</span><br><span class="hljs-string">baseurl=https://mirrors.aliyun.com/centos/\$releasever/updates/\$basearch/</span><br><span class="hljs-string">gpgcheck=1</span><br><span class="hljs-string">gpgkey=file:///etc/pki/rpm-gpg/RPM-GPG-KEY-CentOS-7</span><br><span class="hljs-string"></span><br><span class="hljs-string">[extras]</span><br><span class="hljs-string">name=CentOS-\$releasever - Extras</span><br><span class="hljs-string">baseurl=https://mirrors.aliyun.com/centos/\$releasever/extras/\$basearch/</span><br><span class="hljs-string">gpgcheck=1</span><br><span class="hljs-string">gpgkey=file:///etc/pki/rpm-gpg/RPM-GPG-KEY-CentOS-7</span><br><span class="hljs-string">EOF</span><br><br>yum clean all<br>yum makecache<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-2-2-更新"><a href="#1-2-2-更新" class="headerlink" title="1.2.2. 更新"></a>1.2.2. 更新</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">yum update -y<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="1-3-EPEL镜像设置"><a href="#1-3-EPEL镜像设置" class="headerlink" title="1.3. EPEL镜像设置"></a>1.3. EPEL镜像设置</h2><h3 id="1-3-1-安装EPEL软件包"><a href="#1-3-1-安装EPEL软件包" class="headerlink" title="1.3.1. 安装EPEL软件包"></a>1.3.1. 安装EPEL软件包</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">yum install -y epel-release<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-3-2-设置国内镜像服务器，加速EPEL软件包下载"><a href="#1-3-2-设置国内镜像服务器，加速EPEL软件包下载" class="headerlink" title="1.3.2. 设置国内镜像服务器，加速EPEL软件包下载"></a>1.3.2. 设置国内镜像服务器，加速EPEL软件包下载</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">sed -e <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;s!^metalink=!#metalink=!g&#x27;</span> \<br>    -e <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;s!^#baseurl=!baseurl=!g&#x27;</span> \<br>    -e <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;s!//download\.fedoraproject\.org/pub!//mirrors.aliyun.com!g&#x27;</span> \<br>    -e <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;s!http://mirrors!https://mirrors!g&#x27;</span> \<br>    -i /etc/yum.repos.d/epel*.repo<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-3-3-创建YUM缓存，减少网络请求"><a href="#1-3-3-创建YUM缓存，减少网络请求" class="headerlink" title="1.3.3. 创建YUM缓存，减少网络请求"></a>1.3.3. 创建YUM缓存，减少网络请求</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">yum makecache<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="1-4-安装常用软件"><a href="#1-4-安装常用软件" class="headerlink" title="1.4. 安装常用软件"></a>1.4. 安装常用软件</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">yum install -y vim-enhanced wget curl yum-utils tree pwgen unzip expect tar xz bash-completion-extras<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="1-5-安装Python3-8"><a href="#1-5-安装Python3-8" class="headerlink" title="1.5. 安装Python3.8+"></a>1.5. 安装Python3.8+</h2><h3 id="1-5-1-安装依赖：OpenSSL-1-1"><a href="#1-5-1-安装依赖：OpenSSL-1-1" class="headerlink" title="1.5.1. 安装依赖：OpenSSL 1.1+"></a>1.5.1. 安装依赖：OpenSSL 1.1+</h3><ul><li><p>安装OpenSSL 1.1+软件包</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">pkg_name=openssl<br>pkg_ver=1.1.1n<br>pkg_rel=1<br>pkg=<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;pkg_name&#125;</span>-<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;pkg_ver&#125;</span><br>tar_name=<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;pkg_name&#125;</span>-<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;pkg_ver&#125;</span>-<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;pkg_rel&#125;</span>.el7.x86_64.tar.gz<br>url=http://dl.cdgeekcamp.com/centos/7/<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;pkg_name&#125;</span>/<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;pkg_ver&#125;</span>/<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;tar_name&#125;</span><br>prefix=/usr/local/<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;pkg&#125;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-built_in">test</span> -d <span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;prefix&#125;</span> || (wget <span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;url&#125;</span> -O /tmp/<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;tar_name&#125;</span> &amp;&amp; tar xf /tmp/<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;tar_name&#125;</span> -C $(<span class="hljs-built_in">dirname</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;prefix&#125;</span>))<br><br><span class="hljs-built_in">rm</span> -f /tmp/<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;tar_name&#125;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>更新动态链接库配置</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">egrep <span class="hljs-string">&quot;^<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;prefix&#125;</span>/lib&quot;</span> /etc/ld.so.conf || (<span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;prefix&#125;</span>/lib&quot;</span> &gt;&gt; /etc/ld.so.conf &amp;&amp; ldconfig)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>确认配置</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">ldconfig -p | grep <span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;prefix&#125;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p><strong>终端输出</strong></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">[root@localhost ~]# ldconfig -p | grep <span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;prefix&#125;</span><br>        libssl.so.1.1 (libc6,x86-64) =&gt; /usr/local/openssl-1.1.1n/lib/libssl.so.1.1<br>        libssl.so (libc6,x86-64) =&gt; /usr/local/openssl-1.1.1n/lib/libssl.so<br>        libcrypto.so.1.1 (libc6,x86-64) =&gt; /usr/local/openssl-1.1.1n/lib/libcrypto.so.1.1<br>        libcrypto.so (libc6,x86-64) =&gt; /usr/local/openssl-1.1.1n/lib/libcrypto.so<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-5-2-安装Python3-8"><a href="#1-5-2-安装Python3-8" class="headerlink" title="1.5.2. 安装Python3.8+"></a>1.5.2. 安装Python3.8+</h3><ul><li><p>设置Python3.8+安装变量</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">pkg_name=python<br>pkg_ver=3.10.5<br>pkg_short_num=3<br>pkg_ver_num=310<br>pkg_rel=1<br>pkg=<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;pkg_name&#125;</span>-<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;pkg_ver&#125;</span><br>tar_name=<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;pkg_name&#125;</span>-<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;pkg_ver&#125;</span>-<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;pkg_rel&#125;</span>.el7.x86_64.tar.gz<br>url=http://dl.cdgeekcamp.com/centos/7/python/3/<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;tar_name&#125;</span><br>prefix=/usr/local/<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;pkg&#125;</span><br>bin_dir=<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;prefix&#125;</span>/bin<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>安装Python3.8+软件包</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">test</span> -d <span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;prefix&#125;</span> || (wget <span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;url&#125;</span> -O /tmp/<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;tar_name&#125;</span> &amp;&amp; tar xf /tmp/<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;tar_name&#125;</span> -C $(<span class="hljs-built_in">dirname</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;prefix&#125;</span>))<br><br><span class="hljs-built_in">rm</span> -f /tmp/<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;tar_name&#125;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>设置Python3.8+的环境变量</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;export PATH=<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;bin_dir&#125;</span>:<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;PATH&#125;</span>&quot;</span> &gt; /etc/profile.d/python<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;pkg_short_num&#125;</span>.sh<br>. /etc/profile<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>确认设置</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">which</span> python<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;pkg_short_num&#125;</span> | grep <span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;prefix&#125;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>终端输出</strong></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">/usr/local/python-3.10.5/bin/python3<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>设置Python3.8+的软链接</p></li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;bin_dir&#125;</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">test</span> -L pip<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;pkg_ver_num&#125;</span> || <span class="hljs-built_in">ln</span> -v -s pip<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;pkg_short_num&#125;</span> pip<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;pkg_ver_num&#125;</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">test</span> -L python<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;pkg_ver_num&#125;</span> || <span class="hljs-built_in">ln</span> -v -s python<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;pkg_short_num&#125;</span> python<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;pkg_ver_num&#125;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> -e <span class="hljs-string">&quot;PIP软链接：pip<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;pkg_ver_num&#125;</span>\nPython3软链接：python<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;pkg_ver_num&#125;</span>&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>测试pip命令<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> -e <span class="hljs-string">&quot;执行命令：pip<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;pkg_ver_num&#125;</span> list\n&quot;</span> &amp;&amp; pip<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;pkg_ver_num&#125;</span> list<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><strong>终端输出</strong><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><br>执行命令：pip310 list<br><br>Package    Version<br>---------- -------<br>pip        22.1.2<br>setuptools 58.1.0<br><br>[notice] A new release of pip available: 22.1.2 -&gt; 24.3.1<br>[notice] To update, run: pip install --upgrade pip<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p><em>若出现输出内的notice，则说明当前pip版本过低，可以执行pip install –upgrade pip来升级pip，下次便不会提醒！</em></p><p><font color=red>注：可能会因为源的问题导致更新pip失败！</font></p><ul><li>这里提供pip换源的方式<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bahs">mkdir -p ~/.pip<br>cat &gt; ~/.pip/pip.conf &lt;&lt;EOF<br>[global]<br>index-url = https://mirrors.aliyun.com/pypi/simple/<br>trusted-host = mirrors.aliyun.com<br><br>[install]<br>use-deprecated=legacy-resolver<br>EOF<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h2 id="1-6-安装命令行编辑工具"><a href="#1-6-安装命令行编辑工具" class="headerlink" title="1.6. 安装命令行编辑工具"></a>1.6. 安装命令行编辑工具</h2><h3 id="1-6-1-XML编辑工具"><a href="#1-6-1-XML编辑工具" class="headerlink" title="1.6.1. XML编辑工具"></a>1.6.1. XML编辑工具</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">yum install -y xmlstarlet<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-6-2-INI和Java-Properties文件编辑工具"><a href="#1-6-2-INI和Java-Properties文件编辑工具" class="headerlink" title="1.6.2 INI和Java Properties文件编辑工具"></a>1.6.2 INI和Java Properties文件编辑工具</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">yum install -y crudini<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="1-7-设置系统时区"><a href="#1-7-设置系统时区" class="headerlink" title="1.7. 设置系统时区"></a>1.7. 设置系统时区</h2><p><em>当前系统时区设置为 中国上海</em></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">yes</span>|<span class="hljs-built_in">cp</span> /usr/share/zoneinfo/Asia/Shanghai /etc/localtime<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="1-8-安装时间同步服务"><a href="#1-8-安装时间同步服务" class="headerlink" title="1.8. 安装时间同步服务"></a>1.8. 安装时间同步服务</h2><p>安装时间同步软件chrony</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">yum install -y chrony<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>设置开机启动</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">systemctl <span class="hljs-built_in">enable</span> chronyd<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>启动时间同步服务</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">systemctl start chronyd<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="1-9-禁用IPv6"><a href="#1-9-禁用IPv6" class="headerlink" title="1.9. 禁用IPv6"></a>1.9. 禁用IPv6</h2><p>永久禁用IPv6，重启后生效</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;net.ipv6.conf.all.disable_ipv6 = 1&quot;</span> &gt;&gt;  /etc/sysctl.conf<br><span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;net.ipv6.conf.default.disable_ipv6 = 1&quot;</span> &gt;&gt;  /etc/sysctl.conf<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="1-10-删除安装日志"><a href="#1-10-删除安装日志" class="headerlink" title="1.10. 删除安装日志"></a>1.10. 删除安装日志</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">rm</span> -f ~/anaconda-ks.cfg  ~/install.log  ~/install.log.syslog<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="1-11-禁用SELINUX"><a href="#1-11-禁用SELINUX" class="headerlink" title="1.11. 禁用SELINUX"></a>1.11. 禁用SELINUX</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> SELINUX=disabled&gt;/etc/selinux/config<br><span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> SELINUXTYPE=targeted&gt;&gt;/etc/selinux/config<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="1-12-设置最大文件句柄"><a href="#1-12-设置最大文件句柄" class="headerlink" title="1.12. 设置最大文件句柄"></a>1.12. 设置最大文件句柄</h2><p><em>也许你听过，”Linux下，一切皆文件”。 文件句柄 种类很多，常见的有普通文件句柄（C语言中 open() 函数返回的就是文件句柄）、网络相关句柄等</em></p><p>永久设置打开文件（句柄）的最大数量，重启后生效</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;*               soft   nofile            65535&quot;</span> &gt;&gt; /etc/security/limits.conf<br><span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;*               hard   nofile            65535&quot;</span> &gt;&gt; /etc/security/limits.conf<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="1-13-优化SSH服务"><a href="#1-13-优化SSH服务" class="headerlink" title="1.13. 优化SSH服务"></a>1.13. 优化SSH服务</h2><ul><li><p>修改SSH服务端配置文件sshd_config，加速登录速度、设置连接保持等</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># SSH连接时，服务端会将客户端IP反向解析为域名，导致登录过程缓慢</span><br>sed -i <span class="hljs-string">&quot;s/#UseDNS yes/UseDNS no/&quot;</span> /etc/ssh/sshd_config<br>sed -i <span class="hljs-string">&quot;s/GSSAPIAuthentication yes/GSSAPIAuthentication no/&quot;</span> /etc/ssh/sshd_config<br>sed -i <span class="hljs-string">&quot;s/GSSAPICleanupCredentials yes/GSSAPICleanupCredentials no/&quot;</span> /etc/ssh/sshd_config<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 登录失败最大尝试次数</span><br>sed -i <span class="hljs-string">&quot;s/#MaxAuthTries 6/MaxAuthTries 10/&quot;</span> /etc/ssh/sshd_config<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 连接保持：服务端每隔N秒发送一次请求给客户端，客户端响应后完成一次连接保持检查</span><br>sed -i <span class="hljs-string">&quot;s/#ClientAliveInterval 0/ClientAliveInterval 30/&quot;</span> /etc/ssh/sshd_config<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 连接保持最大重试次数：服务端发出请求后，超过N次没有收到客户端响应，服务端则断开客户端连接</span><br>sed -i <span class="hljs-string">&quot;s/#ClientAliveCountMax 3/ClientAliveCountMax 10/&quot;</span> /etc/ssh/sshd_config<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>重载SSH服务端配置</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">systemctl reload sshd<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>退出当前Shell，重新登录SSH后，新配置生效</p></li></ul><h2 id="1-14-设置主机名"><a href="#1-14-设置主机名" class="headerlink" title="1.14. 设置主机名"></a>1.14. 设置主机名</h2><h3 id="1-14-1-初始化本地解析设置"><a href="#1-14-1-初始化本地解析设置" class="headerlink" title="1.14.1 初始化本地解析设置"></a>1.14.1 初始化本地解析设置</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;127.0.0.1 localhost localhost.localdomain localhost4 localhost4.localdomain4&#x27;</span> &gt; /etc/hosts<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
